### Other Properties

*   **Natural occurrence:** [Primordial](/Primordial_nuclide). It’s been around.
*   **Crystal structure:**
    *   α-Fe: [body-centered cubic](/Cubic_crystal_system) (bcc). Standard. [cI2](/Pearson_symbol).
